data.description: Here's your chance to own 5 fenced acres of horse property in Aguanga.  This Ranch style home is 2 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, and 1458 square feet of living space. There is a security gate, and the majority of the lot is flat and usable with panoramic views all around. Enjoy miles of riding trails and views of Mt Palomar, Mt Cahuilla, and Idyllwild. The propane tank is owned. Plenty of space for horses or projects. Detached carports fitting your cars, trucks or RV. Extra storage container and sheds on the property as well. The kitchen opens up to living area that boasts a custom wood fireplace and mantel. Nice tile throughout and wood flooring in master bedroom. Back patio is covered with outdoor living area for those relaxing quiet evenings. The current loan is assumable at a 3.875% with New American Funding.
